I can't.

5
00:01:02,395 --> 00:01:05,148
Don't leave your socks lying around!

6
00:01:11,321 --> 00:01:12,781
Um...

7
00:01:13,656 --> 00:01:14,616
Welcome home.

8
00:01:18,828 --> 00:01:20,413
- Mia!
- Wait!

9
00:01:20,497 --> 00:01:21,623
Mia!

10
00:01:24,667 --> 00:01:25,835
Hang on!

11
00:01:27,253 --> 00:01:28,463
<i>Hey, Shinpei!</i>

12
00:01:28,546 --> 00:01:30,632
<i>- Mia!</i>
<i>- That's my shirt!</i>

13
00:01:31,216 --> 00:01:36,429
<i>A story of these three</i>
<i>and their marriage is about to begin.</i>

14
00:01:37,889 --> 00:01:39,516
Two Husbands One Wife.

15
00:01:41,893 --> 00:01:44,187
8 MINUTE WALK FROM NISHI-FUNABASHI STATION

16
