to face this issue together.

210
00:17:04,982 --> 00:17:05,816
Yeah.

211
00:17:06,859 --> 00:17:07,901
You're right.

212
00:17:10,696 --> 00:17:13,490
Then, let's answer on three.

213
00:17:14,074 --> 00:17:15,909
- Is that okay?
- Yeah.

214
00:17:16,952 --> 00:17:18,245
Okay.

215
00:17:18,328 --> 00:17:19,455
Ready?

216
00:17:22,166 --> 00:17:24,918
Do you want to have a threesome?

217
00:17:25,419 --> 00:17:26,628
One, two.

218
00:17:26,712 --> 00:17:27,671
- Yes.
- Yes.

219
00:17:27,755 --> 00:17:28,589
I want to!

220
00:17:29,089 --> 00:17:30,424
<i>The timing was off.</i>

221
00:17:30,507 --> 00:17:31,925
<i>It didn't work.</i>

222
00:17:32,009 --> 00:17:33,802
<i>What? Hang on.</i>

223
00:17:33,886 --> 00:17:35,387
<i>There're two jokers.</i>

224
00:17:35,471 --> 00:17:37,306
<i>Really? How come?</i>

225
00:17:37,389 --> 00:17:42,895
<i>As their next step,</i>
<i>they decided to try going to a love hotel.</i>

226
00:17:45,481 --> 00:17:46,982
<i>It's D-day.</i>

227
00:17:55,616 --> 00:17:57,534
<i>Getting nervous.</i>

228
00:17:57,618 --> 00:18:00,704
By the way, should we
stop by at the convenience store?

229
00:18:01,205 --> 00:18:02,456
The hotel has everything.

230
00:18:02,539 --> 00:18:05,459
Oh, but they might not have enough.

231
00:18:05,542 --> 00:18:07,628
- You mean, condoms!
- Too loud.

232
00:18:07,711 --> 00:18:09,880
I brought loads.

233
00:18:10,422 --> 00:18:13,092
Great job. But why is your bag so big?

234
00:18:13,175 --> 00:18:14,927
I thought we'd try things out.

235
00:18:15,010 --> 00:18:16,261
What things?

236
00:18:17,096 --> 00:18:19,223
<i>Nervous and flustered.</i>

237
00:18:21,475 --> 00:18:24,520
<i>Flustered, bewildered, and confused.</i>

238
00:18:25,104 --> 00:18:26,522
This is it.

239
00:18:33,654 --> 00:18:35,864
<i>Completely flustered.</i>

240
00:18:45,666 --> 00:18:47,209
- See ya.
- H-Hey.

241
00:18:47,292 --> 00:18:49,503
- What? No!
- Please!

242
00:18:49,586 --> 00:18:51,922
We're here already! Just give up!

243
00:18:52,005 --> 00:18:54,842
I can't do this! I just can't!

244
00:18:54,925 --> 00:18:56,009
Takuzo?

245
00:18:56,552 --> 00:18:58,929
No! I'm not letting you go!

246
00:18:59,012 --> 00:19:00,722
Do my best at what?

247
00:19:01,223 --> 00:19:02,182
Ow!

248
00:19:02,266 --> 00:19:03,183
Shinpei!

249
00:19:03,267 --> 00:19:05,978
Ow, it hurts!

250
00:19:09,982 --> 00:19:11,024
Ms. Tenma?

251
00:19:11,108 --> 00:19:13,318
What happened? Should I call the police?

252
00:19:13,402 --> 00:19:15,404
No! No police!

253
00:19:15,487 --> 00:19:18,615
Is it a badger game?
There's no shame. Let's call them.

254
00:19:18,699 --> 00:19:19,741
Don't!

255
00:19:19,825 --> 00:19:21,410
Let me explain.

256
00:19:23,078 --> 00:19:27,708
You're giving in to evil? I'll turn
this guy over to the police myself!

257
00:19:34,423 --> 00:19:36,300
<i>Of all times, they ended up</i>

258
00:19:36,383 --> 00:19:39,845
<i>running into Takuzo's colleague</i>
<i>in a situation like this.</i>

259
00:19:40,387 --> 00:19:41,221
<i>Hi-yah!</i>

260
00:19:43,974 --> 00:19:47,269
<i>What will happen</i>
<i>to their three-person marriage plan?</i>

261
00:19:47,352 --> 00:19:48,270
<i>Aiyah!</i>

262
00:19:49,771 --> 00:19:50,856
<i>Sounds interesting.</i>

263
00:19:50,939 --> 00:19:51,899
Paw.

264
00:19:52,399 --> 00:19:53,317
